        Parameters:

        value - the actual value (for xml data xml for binary data is should be base64 encoded data)
        schema - schema if applicable otherwise null
        encoding - encoding if not the default encoding (for default encoding set it to null) (i.e. binary data, use base64)
        mimeType - mimetype of the data, has to be set
